      • getUserAgentDesiredCapabilities

        public org.openqa.selenium.remote.DesiredCapabilities getUserAgentDesiredCapabilities(SauceLabsCapabilitiesConfiguration caps,
                                                                                      java.lang.String deviceName,
                                                                                      java.lang.String userAgent)
        To storing chrome mobile emulation configurations(width, height, pixelRatio and with sauce lab capabilities) and returning the capabilities

        if required feasible result then set relevant parameter from MobileEmulationUserAgentConfiguration()

        Parameters:
        caps - with sauce lab capabilities
        deviceName - name of the device needs to set user agent configuration
        userAgent - to passing the user agent string value depends on device
        Returns:
        uaCaps consist of sauce lab and user agent capabilities

      • setChromeOption

        public org.openqa.selenium.remote.DesiredCapabilities setChromeOption(org.openqa.selenium.chrome.ChromeOptions options)
        Adding sauce lab capabilities to user agent configuration and returning the both capabilities
        Parameters:
        options - ChromeOptions
        Returns:
        sauceWithChromeCab returning the sauce lab capabilities with chrome mobile emulation capabilities
